{"tid":892127,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[求助]offer 2揀1 - ibank BO vs 中資 FO","createTime":"2018-11-06T16:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T15:47:47.000Z","uid":56995,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5988e81e40d4f646e4d49d87b109d323b3b48cc8","tid":892127,"uid":56995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"借朋友acct出post, 小弟做左2年嘢，本身係一間外資BB ibank 入面做緊risk related 既MO/BO. 做得唔錯，老闆亦幾睇我。但我就一直想轉去做IBD FO (I.e. DCM, ECM ) 咁最近就in左一間2nd tier中資行FO，佢出左offer俾我，雖然人工就同我expected 差左啲啲，但個department head 都好有誠意。問題就黎啦，係我想resign 前幾日，老闆突然話我知，想升我。咁我就覺得難得有個咁好既boss, 但又難得有機會轉FO<br />\n<br />\n利申: Preference 我其實冇，淨係想搵多啲錢。given that 2間人工差唔多<br />\n<br />\n1. <br />\nIbank risk BO associate<br />\n21 AL <br />\n6-7pm 收工 (最遲8點)<br />\nBasic 高，接近冇bonus<br />\nTeam culture v chill，自由度好大<br />\n<br />\n2. <br />\n2nd tier 中資 FO analyst <br />\n18 AL<br />\n8- 9pm 收工，(隨時零晨)<br />\nBasic 一般，bonus 高 ( not guarantee la of coz) <br />\n一定chur過之前<br />\n<br />\n如果2間人工 (included bonus) 差唔多，睇發展前景，係咪應該辛苦啲去FO捱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840e899fd04c0b2ab014e31795447434e1e052c5","tid":892127,"uid":56995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:17:19.000Z","msg":"補充多句，舊公司話如果我想做FO可以幫我internal transfer 但唔會做到IBD既FO. 照asso grade, 人工一樣，bonus 都係相差無幾, 多少少。"},{"pid":"56ed46104bb141a1f52e11c135d742e62a4676ed","tid":892127,"uid":96547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:26:13.000Z","msg":"但2nd tier中資FO 你要預返外資難度唔低囉 起碼要再跳去Top tier China boutique <br />\n同埋Market咁差 中資又靠Bonus 自己衡量下 到時頂唔頂到囉<br />\n<br />\n  維持現狀就穩穩定定 有咩事 死都未必死先 但Internal transfer應該都去唔到IBD. skill set完全唔同 你話轉去trading反而有機會<br />\n<br />\n各有利弊<br />\n但我係你的話 我會跳走<br />\n寧為雞口 莫為牛後"},{"pid":"d3a29b9ca07b0fec6446ba446abc63a1196d9d20","tid":892127,"uid":75692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16